OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy day with
OL,6,Fspells of rain or drizzle, perhaps
OL,7,Fturning heavier and more persistent
OL,8,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Less
OL,9,Fwindy than previous days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain or drizzle, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes. Perhaps drier for a time around
OL,15,Fmidnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
