OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloud and rain at first,
OL,6,Fclearing northeast in the morning to
OL,7,Fallow some bright spells. A band of
OL,8,Frain will pass through in the
OL,9,Fafternoon, followed by showers.
OL,10,FOccasionally windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,13,Fwith showers on Friday, windy at
OL,14,Ffirst. Drier with bright spells on
OL,15,FSaturday. Windier again on Sunday with
OL,16,Fvariable cloud with some outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
